data.description: This Charming 3bedroom/2 bath home is located in the Dilworth Estates Subdivision. This brick home exudes character. A quaint kitchen with custom counter cabinetry and granite countertops are designed for both functionality and entertaining. The ample size caters to seamless cooking experiences, making it an ideal space for culinary enthusiasts who love to entertain. The bonus room is great for a playroom or office. Luxurious primary suite boasts walk-in closets, double vanity featuring granite counters, with a relaxing jacuzzi. Step outside to backyard with patio and enjoy summer days by the beautiful pool. A perfect blend of comfort and style awaits you.
